  27:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****   [..]
  28:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****    (#) GPDMA and HPDMA are made available on this series.
  29:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        Transfer could be done thanks to AXI or AHB ports.
  30:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c **** 
  31:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        HPDMA support transmission through:
  32:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****          AXI port 0.
  33:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****          AHB port 1.
  34:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        GPDMA allows transmission through:
  35:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****          GPDMA_P = port-0.
  36:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****          GPDMA_M = port-1
  37:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c **** 
  38:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        The supported configurations for GPDMA and HPDMA can be found
  39:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        in the Connectivity matrix table of the reference manual.
  40:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        Mind that DTCM and ITCM can be only be accessed thanks to HPDMA
  41:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****        AXI port 0.
  42:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****     [..]
