  44:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Normal transfers (legacy)
  45:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Linked-list transfers
